This repository contains various presentations.

Most of the material in these presentations is a collection of bits and pieces from around the net, including other presentations, articles etc.
I'll try to list all sources here, if you see that I've missed some source please let me know!



Sources:
Learn You Some Erlang - http://learnyousomeerlang.com/
"Introduction to Elixir" by Alan Peabody - http://alanpeabody.com/presentations/introduction-to-elixir/
"Introduction to Erlang" by asceth - http://www.slideshare.net/asceth/intro-to-erlang-presentation
"Erlang: A Generalized TCP Server" by Jesse Farmer - http://20bits.com/article/erlang-a-generalized-tcp-server